when our son--

189
00:11:44.005 --> 00:11:45.006
Jake!

190
00:11:47.510 --> 00:11:50.178
I'm in this place
where I have nothing.

191
00:11:51.313 --> 00:11:54.049
Not my people.
not my forest.

192
00:11:55.383 --> 00:11:57.352
Even my father's bow
is gone.

193
00:12:00.322 --> 00:12:01.456
All I have  &

194
00:12:02.857 --> 00:12:04.092
