you're the man!

206
00:12:57.312 --> 00:12:59.781
[rumbles]

207
00:13:04.119 --> 00:13:06.187
[tulkun vocalizing]

208
00:13:24.507 --> 00:13:25.541
Whoa. Bro. Bro.

209
00:13:26.174 --> 00:13:27.208
[exclaims]

210
00:13:28.910 --> 00:13:31.346
