211
00:13:33.516 --> 00:13:35.584
-Whoo! Whoo!
-Whoo-hoo!

212
00:13:37.553 --> 00:13:39.187
Whoo!

213
00:13:41.890 --> 00:13:43.958
-[laughs]
-[screams]

214
00:13:45.994 --> 00:13:47.829
-Whoo! [laughs]
-Bro. come on! Go. go. go. go!

215
00:13:48.363 --> 00:13:50.231
-Oh. sh  &
-Yeah!

216
00:13:55.303 --> 00:13:57.005
That was insane. cuz.

217
00:13:57.072 --> 00:13:58.206
I know. right. Bro?

218
