-[Jake] Hey. hey! Where is it?

243
00:15:03.371 --> 00:15:04.906
-Come on. Come on. Come on.
-I got it. Dad.

244
00:15:05.306 --> 00:15:07.041
-Dad. I found it.
-Hurry.

245
00:15:09.277 --> 00:15:10.579
