246
00:15:10.646 --> 00:15:12.147
-[breathing heavily]
-[air hisses]

247
00:15:12.213 --> 00:15:13.982
Spider. no.

248
00:15:14.048 --> 00:15:15.049
Breathe.

249
00:15:15.116 --> 00:15:17.051
-Breathe.
-Breathe.

250
00:15:17.118 --> 00:15:18.420
