251
00:15:19.120 --> 00:15:20.288
Deep and slow.

252
00:15:20.656 --> 00:15:22.157
There you go.
You're okay.

253
00:15:22.223 --> 00:15:25.326
[breathing deeply] I'm good.
I'm good. I'm okay.

254
00:15:27.429 --> 00:15:29.565
<i>Skxawng.</i>
You have to be careful.

255
00:15:30.165 --> 00:15:31.634
